<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
</head>
<body>
  <div id="background-container">
    <img src="https://i.ibb.co/584Pcn2/logo.png" alt="Agility">
    <div id="modal-container">
      <div id="content">
        <h4 id="title">Olá, {{ name }}!</h4>
        <p class="paragraph-content">
          Falta pouco para você começar a aproveitar oque nossa plataforma pode oferecer,
          para isso clique no botão abaixo para confirmar seu email.
        </p>
        <a
          href="http://localhost:3000/confirm-account?code={{verification_code}}"
        >
        <button type="button" id="button-confirm-email">
          Confirmar email
        </button>
        </a>
        <p class="paragraph-content" id="second-paragraph">
          Caso o botão não funcione você também poderá acessar o link abaixo.
        </p>
        <a
          href="http://localhost:3000/confirm-account?code={{verification_code}}"
          id="link-confirm-email"
        >
          http://localhost:3000/confirm-account?code={{verification_code}}
        </a>
        <footer>
          <p class="paragraph-content">Atenciosamente,</p>
          <p class="paragraph-content">Equipe Agility</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:wght@400;700&family=Roboto:wght@500&display=swap');

    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      outline: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      background-color: #F5F8FA;
    }

    div#background-container {
      background-color: #279AF1;
      width: 100%;
      height: 232px;
      padding: 32px 8px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }

    div#modal-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 32px 16px;
      background-color: #FFFFFF;
      margin: 32px auto;
      border: 1px solid #D4D6D9;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }

    div#content {
      margin: auto;
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 456px;
      width: 100%;
    }

    h4#title {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #333333;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    p.paragraph-content {
      color: #333333;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 24px;
      font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    p#second-paragraph {
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    button#button-confirm-email {
      max-width: 256px;
      width: 100%;
      height: 44px;
      background-color: #279AF1;
      color: #FFFFFF;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 700;
      border: 0;
      border-radius: 5px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background-color 0.2s;
      margin: 32px 0;
    }

    button#button-confirm-email:hover {
      background-color: #0284E5;
    }

    a#link-confirm-email {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #279AF1;
      font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      text-align: left;
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      div#modal-container {
        padding: 24px 16px;
      }

      h4#title {
        font-size: 21px;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
      }

      p.paragraph-content {
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 22px;
      }

      button#button-confirm-email {
        margin: 24px 0;
      }

      a#link-confirm-email {
        font-size: 14px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</body>
</html>
